        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks him for <hi rend="italic">Balanus</hi> specimens. Comments on his findings. A large <hi rend="italic">Acasta</hi> in the wet state would be valuable. Asks JSB to mention his work to J. T. Quekett at the College of Surgeons.</p> 
